      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>Mika+FileScope v2.0.0</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Recursive folder scanning with file type grouping</li>
          <li>Sortable table, donut chart, and bar chart</li>
          <li>CSV and JSON export</li>
          <li>Hidden files toggle</li>
          <li>File category filter</li>
          <li>Timeline with file age histogram</li>
          <li>Duplicate file detection (SHA-256)</li>
          <li>Menubar quick-scan mode</li>
          <li>Sparkle auto-updates</li>
